{"id": "ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1425, "displayName": {"text": "Macy's", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Department store chain providing brand-name clothing, accessories, home furnishings & housewares.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVGNsVTRiMWd3TFV3NVEzbGZNMmRMT0RaUlZVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Love this place and since I live in Altadena I have been a regular since the 90s. Well, I guess we are not the target audience now with these scan barcodes to get prices for certain items... yeah, nah. Why? Why on earth would anyone need to whip out their cell to see something they can read right in front of them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love this place and since I live in Altadena I have been a regular since the 90s. Well, I guess we are not the target audience now with these scan barcodes to get prices for certain items... yeah, nah. Why? Why on earth would anyone need to whip out their cell to see something they can read right in front of them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "wickedseed", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110039611453353539066/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9WsQ79GYCSuAAvZftpA686zmUa01bcuaiFC2t-VHKARffVEbB=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-27T19:46:09.918321269Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVGNsVTRiMWd3TFV3NVEzbGZNMmRMT0RaUlZVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsVGNsVTRiMWd3TFV3NVEzbGZNMmRMT0RaUlZVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35f00665599:0xd269835abbd2d4b0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ016ZHdVR3hOV2pSMVN6Vk1XbTl0TW1jMFdYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very beautiful Macy's location. Many historical items on display.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very beautiful Macy's location. Many historical items on display.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "小艾答案", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110178401799229182789/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN4xXaUmjrSbt5upE7wpMqjchur5yeSiZ8-ANBS92lSwFE7OY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-09T15:39:48.679010899Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ016ZHdVR3hOV2pSMVN6Vk1XbTl0TW1jMFdYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ016ZHdVR3hOV2pSMVN6Vk1XbTl0TW1jMFdYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35f00665599:0xd269835abbd2d4b0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURybVBHeS1nRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My wife and I stopped by this Macy so she could return an item here. We were already in the area so that's why we came to this one. We parked on the roof of the parking structure since all the other parking spots in the garage were taken. So we entered through the top level and had to go down to the lower level to return the item. This Macy is very nice, I think it's the nicest Macy I been to just because of the way they decorate inside. You feel like you're in a high value store based alone on how they display their items. The staff are great here and will answers all your questions.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My wife and I stopped by this Macy so she could return an item here. We were already in the area so that's why we came to this one. We parked on the roof of the parking structure since all the other parking spots in the garage were taken. So we entered through the top level and had to go down to the lower level to return the item. This Macy is very nice, I think it's the nicest Macy I been to just because of the way they decorate inside. You feel like you're in a high value store based alone on how they display their items. The staff are great here and will answers all your questions.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Peter X", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107152190076731796260/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4-iw-e0tHl9zEINryHZo0RHkxSU2aUq1A5Ys5v7J6GgxmO6ZN=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8"}, "publishTime": "2024-07-14T04:19:14.885104Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURybVBHeS1nRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURybVBHeS1nRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35f00665599:0xd269835abbd2d4b0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWJHMUtTVEJtUVc0eFJsQnFkakZUV0dwdE1HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Today's dept. stores leave you longing for the past with 1 exception MACY'S PASADENA is a 1st class dept. store with the BEST store manager in their entire chain of stores. Absolutely the FIRST store on your list to shop at and when you do, you won't need to shop elsewhere.  This store is that GOOD with FANTASTIC PRICES and QUALITY MERCHANDISE  IN EVERY DEPT.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Today's dept. stores leave you longing for the past with 1 exception MACY'S PASADENA is a 1st class dept. store with the BEST store manager in their entire chain of stores. Absolutely the FIRST store on your list to shop at and when you do, you won't need to shop elsewhere.  This store is that GOOD with FANTASTIC PRICES and QUALITY MERCHANDISE  IN EVERY DEPT.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "r a", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100473829250489256165/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9UesXhvjCUIMvcyT9NramTK6hhzzXPBN85eLT9DlRCxbt7g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-17T19:04:47.280725082Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWJHMUtTVEJtUVc0eFJsQnFkakZUV0dwdE1HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s0NWJHMUtTVEJtUVc0eFJsQnFkakZUV0dwdE1HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35f00665599:0xd269835abbd2d4b0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMlpVOWxRM1o2T1RKMmFFWk9ORWR1TVhKTFpGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Yesterday we went to exchange a watch G-Shock and we were in hope of variety , so we encountered Vincent Niemczyk , I hope I’m spelling that right , and he was so wonderfully polite and helpful! He actually showed us that one watch left , 1 G-Shock in the entire store ! But it was definitely the best one thus far ! So we decided to proceed with the exchange, and Vincent was very helpful he even advised us it was 50% off !!!! Wow , we were even more happy with the news ! Vincent not only helped us with our issue and resolved it , but also helped us set up the time on our new watch ! That was so important for us and we didn’t feel rushed or needy , we felt right at home and Vincent had wonderful customer service , which the people at the Glendale location Macys didn’t have !!!! Thank you soooo much Vincent for going above and beyond and a wonderful experience!!! -Ana Fonseca & Martin Ramírez", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Yesterday we went to exchange a watch G-Shock and we were in hope of variety , so we encountered Vincent Niemczyk , I hope I’m spelling that right , and he was so wonderfully polite and helpful! He actually showed us that one watch left , 1 G-Shock in the entire store ! But it was definitely the best one thus far ! So we decided to proceed with the exchange, and Vincent was very helpful he even advised us it was 50% off !!!! Wow , we were even more happy with the news ! Vincent not only helped us with our issue and resolved it , but also helped us set up the time on our new watch ! That was so important for us and we didn’t feel rushed or needy , we felt right at home and Vincent had wonderful customer service , which the people at the Glendale location Macys didn’t have !!!! Thank you soooo much Vincent for going above and beyond and a wonderful experience!!! -Ana Fonseca & Martin Ramírez", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ana Fonseca", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104872613657429610005/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwoWTf91qWZVlqv77fa43YptTDRv48adRxf_qz5IjFA6uRdjZc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-30T23:00:17.767900296Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMlpVOWxRM1o2T1RKMmFFWk9ORWR1TVhKTFpGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMlpVOWxRM1o2T1RKMmFFWk9ORWR1TVhKTFpGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35f00665599:0xd269835abbd2d4b0"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJmVVmAF_DwoARsNTSu1qDadI/photos/AWCwydg1qEd6iihwBrvg89LS2oTsA9PAdhIO1tc1zdbQLiaXStRMrHunK-21z3fMXiO8C13bLRfsJdASMCsUpLKbRVU0TD2nrS0RqK6Tz3JDtoN9SYu_idCaxvvNlYYDE1Mp6prqeVfGAs9nbk0O8SAHCKVWHsFybvpFcy18xIFb_S1xP2phD0OVLtnPmEviYVbWvMpXGvOqSRnrlWTse8wRtBW66a7akX2zrXzh1Y4W3xzi6nsPdjQvtxS5-xlNPLkCKcm74yvbnrCI7dyHh7QJ0SMxzprfYsTU3iIlI8L0I1E8E9BFtMGed7Z1EUIabpG4D3dxOsgP2m9dDYT-rCR8rRIp8PS0zQaTaezHiJazO3Rbl20ZIQk5YDlpCeO5CFO16BBK_23NT-UAlM4h-asKW967rGX8jukRYnx4Fw", "widthPx": 3968, "heightPx": 2976, "authorAttributions": [{